<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
				  <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			      &nbsp; Cecily Fairchild -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">After stage 41 take the Gran Garan route. On stage 43 have Seabrook convince Cecily</font>&nbsp;
			      <br>&nbsp; Elpeo Puru -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">On stage 41, go with the Lean Horse. Convince her with Judau on stage 43. She will join automatically on the other paths</font>&nbsp;
			      <br>&nbsp; Giant Max -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Defeat Millia with Max on stage 40. Attack but do not kill her with Max on stage 61</font>&nbsp;
  			      <br>&nbsp; Giant Millia -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Defeat Millia with Max on stage 40. Attack but do not kill her with Max on stage 61</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Ingram Plisken -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Convince him with Ryusei on the last stage</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Millia Faryna Jenius -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Defeat Millia with Max on stage 40. Do the same on stage 61</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Puru Two -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Get Puru. Go on the Ra Cailum path on stage 50. Convince her with Judau and then Puru on stage 52. Convince and then her with Judau on stage 56</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Quess Paraya -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">During stage 50, choose to go on the Ra Cailum path, then choose to answer as Char in stage 51. On stage 52, convince Quess with Quattro</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Sara Zabiarof -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">When she first appears, attack her with Katsu. On stage 54, convince her with Katsu</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Touji Suzuhara -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Choose to fight Bardiel and get its HP below 50%</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Zechs Merquise -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">On stage 13, agree with Zechs. At stage 57, go on the Angel Halo route and defeat Zechs when he appears</font>&nbsp;<br>
				  <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">GAMESHARK CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			      &nbsp; Infinite HP Mazinger Z -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8013A3EE 270F<br>8013A698 270F</font>&nbsp;
			      <br>&nbsp; Infinite HP Aphrodite A -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>801384FC 270F<br>80138252 270F</font>&nbsp;
			      <br>&nbsp; Infinite & Max HP Kouji Kabuto -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80139B64 270F<br>801398BA 270F</font>&nbsp;
			      <br>&nbsp; Infinite HP GaoGaiGar -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>80139C76 270F<br>80139F20 270F</font>&nbsp;
			      <br>&nbsp; Infinite HP Boss Borot -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8013860E 270F<br>801388B8 270F</font>&nbsp;<br><br>	
	 </tr>
	</table>
